    "description": "<strong>Chromatic Chaos is a roguelite strategy game! </strong><br><br>Piece together a defensive wall out of randomized tiles to protect yourself from hordes of enemies! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129350/extras/0962e447c7c5e2cac8d90390ece3167c.avif?t=1728962358\" width=500 height=500 /></span><br><br>Blast your enemies to pieces, or get your defenses to do it for you! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129350/extras/1873bdf6a1ad80fcc0e9bdbd08dab510.avif?t=1728962358\" width=500 height=500 /></span><br><br>Fight a variety of extraordinarily difficult bosses! <br>(Maybe some not so difficult...) <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129350/extras/6d5116cdf8ef9e714f974a2baa4561ad.avif?t=1728962358\" width=500 height=500 /></span><br><br>Combine a plethora of items to create satisfying synergies, or break the game entirely! <br>(Please report any bugs and exploits to the developer in the discord!) <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129350/extras/1a6dec5fa977a324e508c58821c7455f.avif?t=1728962358\" width=500 height=500 /></span><br><br>Warning! May include clowns!",
